  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Node.js</title>

    <para>
      <application>Node.js</application> is a
      <application>JavaScript</application> runtime built on
      <application>Chrome's</application> V8 JavaScript engine.
    </para>

    &lfs130_checked;

